      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nPassed enforced test review-ldiskfs-arm on CentOS 7.0/x86_64, CentOS 8.0/aarch64 uploaded by AT Release Candidate from trevis-79vm33: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/12930ac5-5983-4c22-917c-70f181bcd918 ran 5 tests.",
